<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 00:50:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国针对中国生物科技公司药明康德、华大基因的法案被推迟</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-bill-targeting-chinese-biotech-firms-wuxi-apptec-bgi-hits-delay-2024-02-02/</link><description>一名参议院助手和其他三名消息人士周五表示，美国国会一项引发中国药明康德股票抛售的法案本周在参议院被推迟。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 22:34:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-bill-targeting-chinese-biotech-firms-wuxi-apptec-bgi-hits-delay-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国公布与伊朗石油网络有关的指控和扣押</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-announces-charges-seizures-linked-irans-illicit-oil-trafficking-network-doj-2024-02-02/</link><description>美国周五宣布了与一个价值数十亿美元的石油贩运网络有关的恐怖主义和逃避制裁指控，并称该网络为伊朗精英伊斯兰革命卫队（IRGC）和其他激进组织提供资金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 18:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-announces-charges-seizures-linked-irans-illicit-oil-trafficking-network-doj-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>完成恒大废弃房屋的道路不平坦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/uneven-path-finish-evergrandes-abandoned-housing-chinese-city-2024-02-02/</link><description>在中国北方城市石家庄的市中心，一堵写着“快乐每一天”标语的栅栏里隐藏着一座未完工的公寓大楼，每天都在提醒着人们，中国曾经最大的开发商倒闭所带来的未解决的成本。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 14:07:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/uneven-path-finish-evergrandes-abandoned-housing-chinese-city-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国法院阻止佛罗里达州禁止中国公民拥有财产的法律</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-blocks-florida-law-barring-chinese-citizens-owning-property-2024-02-02/</link><description>美国一家上诉法院阻止佛罗里达州对两名在该法律通过时正在购买房产的中国公民执行禁止中国公民在该州拥有房屋或土地的禁令。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 13:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-blocks-florida-law-barring-chinese-citizens-owning-property-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>独家：阿里巴巴考虑出售包括盒马鲜生、大润发在内的消费资产——消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibaba-considers-sale-consumer-assets-including-freshippo-rt-mart-sources-2024-02-02/</link><description>三位知情人士称，中国互联网巨头阿里巴巴集团正在寻求出售多项消费行业资产，包括食品杂货业务盒马鲜生和零售商大润发。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 13:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibaba-considers-sale-consumer-assets-including-freshippo-rt-mart-sources-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>Raizen与中国比亚迪将在巴西建设电动汽车充电站网络</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/raizen-chinas-byd-build-ev-charging-station-network-brazil-2024-02-02/</link><description>糖和乙醇公司 Raizen 和中国汽车制造商比亚迪周五表示，两家公司正在联手在巴西八个城市创建一个由 600 个电动汽车 (EV) 充电站组成的网络。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 12:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/raizen-chinas-byd-build-ev-charging-station-network-brazil-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>苹果在华销量暴跌凸显本土品牌影响力减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-china-sales-tumble-highlights-waning-clout-local-brands-gain-2024-02-02/</link><description>作为全球最大的智能手机市场，中国对于苹果的销量增长至关重要。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 11:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-china-sales-tumble-highlights-waning-clout-local-brands-gain-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于担心美国生物技术法案，中国药明康德和药明生物股价跌至多年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-wuxi-apptec-wuxi-biologics-plunge-multi-year-lows-fears-over-us-biotech-2024-02-02/</link><description>由于投资者对美国针对中国生物科技巨头的法案草案的担忧加剧，药明康德有限公司和药明生物（开曼）的股价周五暴跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 09:57:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-wuxi-apptec-wuxi-biologics-plunge-multi-year-lows-fears-over-us-biotech-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国新的房地产融资措施将面临银行谨慎态度的考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/new-china-property-financing-measures-set-be-tested-by-banks-cautious-approach-2024-02-02/</link><description>作为支持措施的一部分，中国计划在未来几天增加住宅项目的融资，但银行不愿向受危机打击的行业提供贷款，这仍将是最需要新资金的陷入困境的开发商的主要障碍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 07:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/new-china-property-financing-measures-set-be-tested-by-banks-cautious-approach-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>腾讯砍掉 Square Enix 的《尼尔》手机游戏，寻找新的热门游戏 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-axes-square-enix-nier-mobile-game-it-hunts-new-hit-sources-2024-02-02/</link><description>据三名知情人士透露，腾讯去年 12 月停止了一款基于 Square Enix 的《尼尔》系列的备受期待的手机游戏的开发，这标志着这家中国游戏巨头寻找新热门游戏的进程遭遇挫折。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 05:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-axes-square-enix-nier-mobile-game-it-hunts-new-hit-sources-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国就业报告井喷，收益率和美元上涨，股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-02/</link><description>周五，美国就业报告井喷，打破了近期降息的预期，并凸显了强劲的经济，美国国债收益率大幅上涨，美元飙升，世界股市上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 02:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>日本向唐纳德·特朗普传达的信息：不要与中国达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-message-donald-trump-dont-cut-deal-with-china-2024-02-02/</link><description>最近几周，东京加大了与特朗普关系密切人士的接触力度。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 01:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-message-donald-trump-dont-cut-deal-with-china-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国销售滞后，苹果 iPhone 目标比华尔街目标低数十亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-quarterly-profit-revenue-top-wall-street-targets-china-lags-2024-02-01/</link><description>苹果公司周四预测，由于中国业务受到打击，iPhone 销量将下降，总收入目标将低于华尔街预期 60 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 21:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-quarterly-profit-revenue-top-wall-street-targets-china-lags-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国要求乌克兰将其公司从“战争赞助者”名单中删除</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-warns-ukraine-over-naming-its-firms-sponsors-war-sources-2024-02-01/</link><description>中国周四要求乌克兰立即将十几家中国公司从被指定为“国际战争赞助者”的公司名单中删除，并表示希望基辅“消除负面影响”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 11:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-warns-ukraine-over-naming-its-firms-sponsors-war-sources-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>旅游业复苏，香港 12 月零售额增长 7.8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-dec-retail-sales-up-78-tourism-recovers-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四官方数据显示，由于旅游业持续改善，香港 12 月份零售额连续 13 个月增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 09:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-dec-retail-sales-up-78-tourism-recovers-2024-02-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>